                <note>It ends abruptly, on fol. 137 a, with the words of the explicit above (p. cl., at the foot), and the scribe has added a note on the lower margin.<!--To be put into an addition and linked: ܥܕܡܐ ܠܗܪܟܐ ܐܫܟ̣ܚܢܢ ܒܢܘܣܟܐ ܗܕܐ ܬܫܥܝܬܐ. ܠܐ ܬܥ̣ܕܠܘܢ ܠܟ̇ܬܘܒܐ ܫܝ̣ܛܐ-->
