                      <persName>ܦܪܐܦܝܣܛܝܣ ܪܘܡܠܘܣ</persName>
                    </quote>) under<persName>Trajan</persName>; and of the<persName>Comes Eudoxius, surnamed Marianus</persName>(<quote xml:lang="syr">
